General.Name: Suzhou UIGreen Micro & Nano Technologies Co. Ltd. A
General.Description: Suzhou UIGreen Micro&Nano Technologies Co.,Ltd engages in the research and development, production, and sale of micro-electromechanical (MEMS) fine components and semiconductor test probe products in China and internationally. It offers shielding cover, micro connectors and components, precision structural parts, MEMS acoustics, pressure sensors, optics, and semiconductor test consumables. The company's micro components products are widely used in chip packaging and testing, TWS earphones, smartphones, hearing aids, and other high-tech end products. Suzhou UIGreen Micro&Nano Technologies Co.,Ltd was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in Suzhou, China.
